📁 Project 2: Combined To-Do List and Dynamic Image Gallery
📝 Title: Interactive To-Do List & Dynamic Image Gallery (JavaScript DOM Project)
📋 Description:
This project combines two interactive features on a single page: a dynamic to-do list and an image gallery. Both components are built using vanilla JavaScript and showcase DOM manipulation, event handling, and responsive styling.

💡 Features:
Add and remove to-do list items dynamically

Add and remove images using valid URLs

Responsive layout for mobile and desktop

Clean and user-friendly design

All functionality built without external libraries

🚀 How to Use:
Clone or download the repository

Open index.html in your browser

Try adding tasks and images dynamically

Remove items with a single click

🛠️ Tech Stack:
HTML5

CSS3

JavaScript (DOM, events)
